  m_Name: ReduceTheSupportEvent
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WarForOilEvent
  id: wfo_ofpc_02
  displayName: Reduce War Support Offer
  description: 'The opposing country offers you a sum of money to reduce your country''s
    support for the war.

    The proposal aims to temporarily cut your military
    and logistical contribution.

    Your decision may shift the balance of the
    conflict in the short term.

    This move could give the enemy time to recover.'
  devNote: 
  eventNote: "d\xFC\u015Fman \xFClke para kar\u015F\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131nda kendi
    \xFClkemize deste\u011Fi k\u0131smam\u0131z\u0131 teklif eder kabul edilirse
    ele ke\u015F para ge\xE7er ancak siyasi n\xFCfuz ve itibar kaybederiz \u015F\xFCphe
    art\u0131\u015F\u0131 olur\n\nveya d\xFCzg\xFCnce reddedip sava\u015Fa devam
    ederiz \n\nveya teklifi if\u015Fa ederiz ancak daha sonra ate\u015Fkes istemenin
    \xF6n\xFC kapan\u0131r(eventlerle ate\u015Fkese ba\u011Flanmak hala m\xFCmk\xFCn)"
